quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  17,94,"Ndipo palibe chimene chidawaletsa anthu kukhala okhulupirira pamene malangizo adadza kwa iwo koma mwano chifukwa iwo amati, “Kodi Mulungu watumiza munthu kukhala Mtumwi?”"
  17,95,"Nena, “Ngati angelo akadakhala pa dziko lapansi, namayenda mwamtendere, ndithudi, Ife tikadatumiza kwa iwo mngelo kuchoka kumwamba ngati Mtumwi.”"
  17,96,"Nena, “Mulungu ndi wokwana kukhala mboni pakati pa ine ndi inu. Ndithudi! Iye ndi wodziwa ndi woona zonse za akapolo ake.”"
  17,97,"Ndipo aliyense amene Mulungu wamutsogolera , atsogozedwa bwino koma iye amene Iye amusocheza wotere iwe siungamupezere mtetezi wina aliyense kupatula Iye yekha. Ndipo Ife tidzawasonkhanitsa onse pa tsiku la kuuka kwa akufa, akuyenda pa nkhope zawo, akhungu, abububu ndi agonthi, malo awo adzakhala Gahena ndipo pamene malawi ake azikazima tizidzawaonjezera moto"
  17,98,"Amenewo ndiwo malipiro awo chifukwa iwo sadakhulupirire mawu athu ndipo adati, “Pamene ife tidzasanduka mafupa ndi kufufutika, kodi tidzaukitsidwa kukhala chilengedwe chatsopano?”"
  17,99,Kodi iwo saona kuti Mulungu amene adalenga kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi ali ndi mphamvu yolenga zofanana ndi iwo? Ndipo Iye adawaikira iwo nthawi yosakayikitsa. Komabe anthu ochimwa amakana choonadi ndikusankha kusakhulupirira
  17,100,"Nena, “Ngati mukadakhala ndi nkhokwe za chifundo cha Ambuye wanga, ndithudi, inu mukanazibisa poopa kuti zingathe.” Ndithudi munthu ndi waumbombo"